Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.63,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.34,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}be they criminals or actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.02,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A robbery that happened before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The cornered culprit crosses through space and time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.17,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:29.69,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Created by\NGosho Aoyama\N"Detective Conan"\NSerialized in Shogakukan's\N'Weekly Shonen Sunday'
