Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Doc his cell phone saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So she didn't figure out your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:19.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran doesn't think I'm Shin'ichi Kudo anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:24.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the whole idea that a drug turned me into a little kid is so unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised she almost figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to thank me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:34.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who sent all those childish text messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it look like Agasa's phone was really yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, she doesn't suspect you anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this morning was just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.60,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You're so smart, Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.53,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here! A big helping for the future sleuth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, listen! It's Shin'ichi's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:06.99,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi Kudo here! Please leave a message after the beep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave her your cell number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I set it on voice mail whenever I'm with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All well and good, but don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me, I'm not about to get Ran involved with the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot stronger than you think she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.94,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.98,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean her karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:43.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he can't decide whether to go into that store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's gonna rob the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:19.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far more likely he's just going to buy a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be for anyone. His mom, a sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when a man goes into a jewelry store with a face that red,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's gotta be for a woman he's trying to impress, or a girlfriend he wants to please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}80,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It sure is expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And I still haven't finished paying for that ring I lost at the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.72,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.22,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I caught Miwako staring at this brooch like it was Japan's most wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.35,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If you want to wow her, this is the one to buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.14,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But remember, don't tell her I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:05:00.15,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If she thinks it's a coincidence, it'll deepen your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for one of your children, we can adjust the size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Go for this necklace with all the diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a bit too glitzy for Detective Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How long have you kids been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Detective Sato's birthday is in April...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So her birthstone's diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's perfect! Buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say I was getting anything for Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I take a look at that brooch, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the design!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Sato's so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A jewel robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NHurry! Your tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A tranquilizer dart won't go through that helmet or that heavy coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't tell if the gun is real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my Power Kick Shoes{cf #5} in this situation either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This neighborhood is swarming with plain-clothes detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're smart, you'll drop your gun and turn yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's all the detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off-duty myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going into that alley...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right here, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,drop your gun, and calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something fall?{previously "Did something happen?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what was that loud noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:53.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Somebody go up and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:07.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? I heard something fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, er, please don't move the truck or its contents
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until the ambulance and police arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Its contents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disturb the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish moving this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until the ambulance arrives, but after that I've gotta get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to the person who hired you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? He's probably in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, call him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's here for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've barely moved anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems a guy fell on our truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we have to put this delivery on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hurry up and do whatever you cops have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a schedule to keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's our fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't cornered him on that rooftop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't have jumped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just five kids and one unarmed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the robber thought he was cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:32.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he could've turned back and broken his way through at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:36.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he was planning to commit suicide from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else he thought he'd survive that fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,makes me suspect it's not an ordinary robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or an ordinary suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just {\i1}happened{\i0} to bump into a jewelry store robbery in progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and when you went after the guy, he jumped off a building?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He vaulted over the barrier around the rooftop,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and fell on top of this truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An overzealous police officer kills a suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:23.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it. The media will eat us for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't over-jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just chasing the robber like he was supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we got to the roof, the robber went crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened so fast, we couldn't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He jumped off the roof with no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as if he'd planned it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you kids in the jewelry store when the robber attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! We saw Detective Takagi go into the store and we followed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a jewelry store on your off hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, er, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you were into jewelry, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get what you went in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The robber stole it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He surprised Ayumi and she dropped it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:38.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He put it in the pocket of his coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it should still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a weird thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you showed up, I climbed up and checked the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't find that brooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A brooch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A present for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure he threw it away or dropped it while running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it fell out of his pocket when he jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you can forget about that brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we find it, it'll have to be kept as evidence for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And who'd want a piece of jewelry with such a gruesome past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's nothing wrong with the brooch itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can just wipe off the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's other weird stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The robber was wearing a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But after the fall, his head was smashed open,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like he'd taken the helmet off in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:56.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And back at the store, when you said you were a cop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the robber...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like he {\i1}wanted{\i0} the police to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was that cocky, he must have had a perfect escape plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or he thought he could survive jumping off a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why he took his helmet off? Was it part of his plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we need to find the identity of this robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, you can't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he looks like someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:39.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I run a restaurant in the neighborhood. He's in all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he worked for Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s company...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekota...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:51.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The truck the robber fell on was moving office equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for Nekota, that man over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he does work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Until last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worked for me since I started my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're in the middle of tough times, so I had to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was part of our restructuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:24.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he was driven to do {\i1}this{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to downsize your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The office space in this building is smaller and the rent is cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was your company before this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The top floor of that building there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right across the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a look at your old office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's been planning this robbery for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he may have left evidence in the old office space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you met these detectives before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything wrong in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was his locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this was his desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got a lot of stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the new space to represent a fresh start,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I left the old furniture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't see anything in his locker that might connect to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in the desk either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:45.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fired him a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how come all his belongings are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to upset the other employees with the news that he'd been laid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell them he was on a business trip until we got the new office running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Atomura to come back after we moved and collect his things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the truck the robber fell on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the truck's down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be across from the building the robber jumped from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the robber was trying to jump to this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:22.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:25.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gap is almost 9 meters across,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the robber was carrying a heavy bag full of jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you were Kamen Yaiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd never try a stunt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Kamen Yaiba would never steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, where were you when the movers were moving things out of this office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, in my apartment downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You live under the balcony we were just on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:06.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The office was on the ninth floor, four floors above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny-looking helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bicycle racing helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I used to do triathlons when I was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seen enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:23.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Atomura for a long time, but you won't find anything connected to him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:37.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the police were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a robbery just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if this had anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:50.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Isaka. I live on the sixth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days ago, around 2 AM, I woke up to a heavy thudding sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:19:01.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a thin, stick-like shadow projected against the curtain by the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:08.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke my husband up and went out onto the balcony, but it was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband says I was dreaming, but I thought I should tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you live over this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Room 605, right above this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:26.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that same sound at the time of the robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I was watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know anything about the robbery until I heard the police sirens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:33.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get back to work already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:42.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still need to make a bunch of round trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How much stuff have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:50.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I expanded my company too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to cover the entire ninth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:58.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells fishy here, but there's no reason not to rule is a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've taken pictures of the crime scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we've got all the evidence, except that brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the fake gun and stolen jewels in the bag near the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no reason to hold up the movers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep the plastic sheet on top of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:20.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll need to confiscate the truck when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:32.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you started carrying stuff down to the truck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where did you park?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the back door of this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the opposite side from the street with the new building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:43.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we drove around a back alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The from that sewer construction they've been doing all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Lots of noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:04.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A narrow back alley that not many people use...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:09.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of noise, that Nekota guy was a pain in the rear too, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! He insisted on giving us exact procedures for moving his stuff out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He made everyone, even the driver, come up to the office for a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we got there, he kept us waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he cancelled twice, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally we were going to do the move two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he called that morning and told us he'd had a sudden{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was a perfect day to move! Nice and sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did tell us beforehand that he might need to reschedule the move,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he paid us for all three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it was good pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I hope I never land a client like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister! Good luck with the moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:50.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Bedroom, bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:00.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If my deductions are correct, it's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:09.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes! It's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I knew it. This was no suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:23.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nekota murdered Atomura and covered up his crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:31.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}by jumping through time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:04.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you yelled at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:10.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:12.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:18.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know we're key witnesses to the jewelry store robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:22.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:30.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:35.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
